#### PC'lerin netplan Ayarları

uPC1 netplan ayarları
```yaml
# uPC1 
network:
  version: 2
  renderer: networkd
  ethernets: 
    enp0s3:
      dhcp4: yes
    enp0s8:
      dhcp4: no
      addresses:
      - 192.168.1.1/24
      gateway4: 192.168.1.254
      nameservers:
          addresses: [8.8.8.8, 1.1.1.1]
      routes:
      - to: 192.168.0.0/16
        via: 192.168.1.254
```

